\c 173 

\s Guh 133 NYEMERERA NGENDANE NAWE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Nyemerera ngendane nawe, Mana, nk’ukw Enoki yagenje. Nyoboresh’ ukuboko kwawe, unyerekez’ ah’ushaka hose. Nubw’ inzir’ itagaragara, nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Nta bwo nahangara kugenda ntari kumwe nawe, Mukiza;\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Nagoswe n’abanz’ igihumbi; dor’ imitegw\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd  intaye hagati.\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Burije rwose, ntihabona; nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ni nguma \bd*\bd Mu \bd*\bd maboko yawe, sinzaba ncyitaye ku by’isi;\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Nta kindi nziratana rwose\bd*\bd ,\bd*\bd  keretse wa musaraba wawe\bd*\bd . \bd*\bd Ngez’ubwo nzager’i Sioni; nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.\bd*
